// SessionCard
// Card displaying a collab session's name, phase badge, last-modified time, and item count.

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(timestamp) -> string
  Converts a numeric timestamp to a relative string ("just now", "5m ago", "2h ago", etc.).

---

FUNCTION SessionCard(props) -> ReactNode                                  EXPORT
  Renders a clickable card with the session name, phase badge (color-coded), relative last-modified time, and item count.
  Highlights with an accent ring when isSelected is true.
  Calls onClick when clicked.
